==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*αὐξάνω / auxanō / owx-an'-o

===Etymology===
*A prolonged form of a primary verb; to grow (“wax”), that is, enlarge (literally or figuratively, actively or passively): 

===Verb===
'''αὐξάνω'''

# [[grow]] (up), (give the) [[increase]].

